\"true\">03</span><div><p class=\"font-display text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-[2.6rem] font-light text-white group-hover:text-champagne transition-colors duration-300 leading-tight\">Gestion administrative</p><p class=\"font-body text-xs sm:text-sm text-white/28 mt-1.5 group-hover:text-white/50 transition-colors duration-300\">Facturation, suivi des flux et domiciliation d&#x27;entreprise.</p></div></div><div class=\"shrink-0 ml-4\"><div class=\"w-9 h-9 sm:w-10 sm:h-10 rounded-full border border-white/[0.08] flex items-center justify-center text-white/20 group-hover:border-champagne/35 group-hover:text-champagne transition-all duration-300 group-hover:scale-110\"><svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><line x1=\"5\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"19\" y2=\"12\"></line><polyline points=\"12 5 19 12 12 19\"></polyline></svg></div></div></a><a class=\"group flex items-center justify-between py-7 sm:py-9 border-b border-white/[0.05] hover:border-champagne/25 transition-colors duration-300\" href=\"/fr/services/gestion-immobiliere\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-6 sm:gap-12\"><span class=\"font-body text-[10px] tracking-[0.20em] text-white/18 font-medium w-5 shrink-0 select-none group-hover:text-champagne/50 transition-colors duration-300\" aria-hidden=\"true\">04</span><div><p class=\"font-display text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-[2.6rem] font-light text-white group-hover:text-champagne transition-colors duration-300 leading-tight\">Gestion Immobilière</p><p class=\"font-body text-xs sm:text-sm text-white/28 mt-1.5 group-hover:text-white/50 transition-colors duration-300\">Gestion locative, suivi financier et accompagnement juridique.</p></div></div><div class=\"shrink-0 ml-4\"><div class=\"w-9 h-9 sm:w-10 sm:h-10 rounded-full border border-white/[0.08] flex items-center justify-center text-white/20 group-hover:border-champagne/35 group-hover:text-champagne transition-all duration-300 group-hover:scale-110\"><svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><line x1=\"5\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"19\" y2=\"12\"></line><polyline points=\"12 5 19 12 12 19\"></polyline></svg></div></div></a></div><div class=\"mt-10 sm:hidden\"><a class=\"btn-outline-dark w-full justify-center\" href=\"/fr/services\">Voir tous nos services<svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><line x1=\"5\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"19\" y2=\"12\"></line><polyline points=\"12 5 19 12 12 19\"></polyline></svg></a></div></div></section><section class=\"relative w-full overflow-hidden bg-mineral\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 1440 80\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute top-0 left-0 w-full pointer-events-none z-0\" style=\"height:var(--slant-h)\"><polygon points=\"0,0 1440,0 0,80\" fill=\"#46184E\"></polygon></svg><div class=\"relative z-10 container-main pt-32 sm:pt-40 pb-28 sm:pb-36\"><div class=\"text-center mb-16 sm:mb-20\"><span class=\"section-label\">Ils nous font confiance</span><h2 class=\"font-display font-light text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl leading-[1.15] tracking-[-0.01em] text-navy\">Ce que disent<!-- --> <span class=\"italic font-light text-champagne\">nos clients</span></h2></div><figure class=\"text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto\"><span class=\"font-display block leading-[0.75] text-gold/[0.13] select-none pointer-events-none -mb-5\" style=\"font-size:clamp(5rem, 12vw, 8rem)\" aria-hidden=\"true\">“</span><blockquote><p class=\"font-display font-light italic text-xl sm:text-[1.6rem] text-ink/80 leading-[1.62]\">SRD Partners a transformé notre approche financière. Grâce à leur expertise pointue, nous avons optimisé notre charge fiscale de manière significative tout en gagnant une visibilité accrue sur nos performances.</p></blockquote><figcaption class=\"mt-8 flex flex-col items-center gap-1.5\"><div class=\"w-8 h-px bg-gold/45 mb-3\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><p class=\"font-body text-sm font-semibold text-navy\">M. Durand</p><p class=\"font-body text-xs text-muted\">Directeur général, PME industrielle</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"flex items-center gap-5 my-14 sm:my-16\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><div class=\"flex-1 h-px bg-black/[0.07]\"></div><div class=\"w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-gold/40\"></div><div class=\"flex-1 h-px bg-black/[0.07]\"></div></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-10 lg:gap-16\"><figure class=\"flex flex-col gap-5\"><svg width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke=\"none\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"text-gold/35\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M3 21c3 0 7-1 7-8V5c0-1.25-.756-2.017-2-2H4c-1.25 0-2 .75-2 1.972V11c0 1.25.75 2 2 2 1 0 1 0 1 1v1c0 1-1 2-2 2s-1 .008-1 1.031V20c0 1 0 1 1 1zm12 0c3 0 7-1 7-8V5c0-1.25-.757-2.017-2-2h-4c-1.25 0-2 .75-2 1.972V11c0 1.25.75 2 2 2h.75c0 2.25.25 4-2.75 4v3c0 1 0 1 1 1z\"></path></svg><blockquote><p class=\"font-display font-light italic text-base sm:text-lg text-ink/70 leading-[1.76]\">Une équipe réactive, disponible et d&#x27;une rigueur exemplaire. Depuis que nous leur avons confié notre comptabilité, nous pouvons nous concentrer pleinement sur notre cœur de métier.</p></blockquote><figcaption class=\"flex items-center gap-3 pt-5 border-t border-black/[0.07]\"><div class=\"w-9 h-9 rounded-full bg-navy text-white flex items-center justify-center font-body text-[10px] font-semibold tracking-[0.08em] shrink-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\">ML</div><div><p class=\"font-body text-sm font-semibold text-navy leading-snug\">Mme Laurent</p><p class=\"font-body text-xs text-muted mt-0.5\">Gérante, Société de services</p></div></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"flex flex-col gap-5\"><svg width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke=\"none\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"text-gold/35\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M3 21c3 0 7-1 7-8V5c0-1.25-.756-2.017-2-2H4c-1.25 0-2 .75-2 1.972V11c0 1.25.75 2 2 2 1 0 1 0 1 1v1c0 1-1 2-2 2s-1 .008-1 1.031V20c0 1 0 1 1 1zm12 0c3 0 7-1 7-8V5c0-1.25-.757-2.017-2-2h-4c-1.25 0-2 .75-2 1.972V11c0 1.25.75 2 2 2h.75c0 2.25.25 4-2.75 4v3c0 1 0 1 1 1z\"></path></svg><blockquote><p class=\"font-display font-light italic text-base sm:text-lg text-ink/70 leading-[1.76]\">L&#x27;accompagnement lors de la création de notre société a été irréprochable. Des professionnels pédagogues et disponibles, qui ont su anticiper chaque étape avec clarté.</p></blockquote><figcaption class=\"flex items-center gap-3 pt-5 border-t border-black/[0.07]\"><div class=\"w-9 h-9 rounded-full bg-navy text-white flex items-center justify-center font-body text-[10px] font-semibold tracking-[0.08em] shrink-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\">FF</div><div><p class=\"font-body text-sm font-semibold text-navy leading-snug\">M. &amp; Mme Favre</p><p class=\"font-body text-xs text-muted mt-0.5\">Fondateurs, Start-up technologique</p></div></figcaption></figure></div></div></section><section class=\"relative bg-navy\"><div class=\"hidden md:block\" style=\"height:400vh\"><div class=\"sticky top-0 h-screen flex flex-col overflow-hidden z-20\"><div class=\"container-main text-center pt-28 pb-8 shrink-0\"><span class=\"section-label text-gold/70\">Notre approche</span><h2 class=\"font-display font-light text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl leading-[1.15] tracking-[-0.01em] text-white mt-2\">Un accompagnement<!-- --> <span class=\"italic font-light text-champagne\">structuré</span></h2></div><div class=\"flex-1 overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"flex h-full will-change-transform\" style=\"width:400vw;backface-visibility:hidden;-webkit-backface-visibility:hidden\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 px-12 lg:px-20\" style=\"width:100vw\"><div class=\"max-w-2xl w-full\"><p class=\"font-display leading-none text-white/[0.035] select-none -mb-6\" style=\"font-size:clamp(5rem, 12vw, 9rem)\" aria-hidden=\"true\">01</p><h3 class=\"font-body text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-light text-white mb-5 leading-[1.2]\">Premier contact</h3><div class=\"h-px w-10 bg-gold/50 mb-6\"></div><p class=\"font-body text-white/55 text-base leading-relaxed mb-8\">Nous prenons le temps de comprendre votre situation, vos objectifs et vos contraintes. Un premier entretien sans engagement vous permet d&#x27;exposer vos besoins et de découvrir notre approche.</p><div><span class=\"section-label text-gold/60 mb-3 block\">Livrables</span><ul class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><li class=\"font-body text-[13px] text-white/65 border border-white/[0.12] rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 bg-white/[0.04]\">Diagnostic initial</li><li class=\"font-body text-[13px] text-white/65 border border-white/[0.12] rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 bg-white/[0.04]\">Proposition sur mesure</li><li class=\"font-body text-[13px] text-white/65 border border-white/[0.12] rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 bg-white/[0.04]\">Devis transparent</li></ul></div></div></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 px-12 lg:px-20\" style=\"width:100vw\"><div class=\"max-w-2xl w-full\"><p class=\"font-display leading-none text-white/[0.035] select-none -mb-6\" style=\"font-size:clamp(5rem, 12vw, 9rem)\" aria-hidden=\"true\">02</p><h3 class=\"font-body text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-light text-white mb-5 leading-[1.2]\">Analyse &amp; Stratégie</h3><div class=\"h-px w-10 bg-gold/50 mb-6\"></div><p class=\"font-body text-white/55 text-base leading-relaxed mb-8\">Nos experts analysent votre situation financière, fiscale et administrative en profondeur. Nous définissons ensemble la stratégie optimale pour atteindre vos objectifs dans les meilleures conditions.</p><div><span class=\"section-label text-gold/60 mb-3 block\">Livrables</span><ul class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><li class=\"font-body text-[13px] text-white/65 border border-white/[0.12] rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 bg-white/[0.04]\">Rapport d&#x27;analyse</li><li class=\"font-body text-[13px] text-white/65 border border-white/[0.12] rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 bg-white/[0.04]\">Plan d&#x27;action détaillé</li><li class=\"font-body text-[13px] text-white/65 border border-white/[0.12] rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 bg-white/[0.04]\">Calendrier d&#x27;exécution</li></ul></div></div></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 px-12 lg:px-20\" style=\"width:100vw\"><div class=\"max-w-2xl w-full\"><p class=\"font-display leading-none text-white/[0.035] select-none -mb-6\" style=\"font-size:clamp(5rem, 12vw, 9rem)\" aria-hidden=\"true\">03</p><h3 class=\"font-body text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-light text-white mb-5 leading-[1.2]\">Mise en œuvre</h3><div class=\"h-px w-10 bg-gold/50 mb-6\"></div><p class=\"font-body text-white/55 text-base leading-relaxed mb-8\">Nous exécutons le plan d&#x27;action avec rigueur et dans les délais convenus. Vous bénéficiez d&#x27;un suivi régulier et d&#x27;une communication proactive à chaque étape clé de la mission.</p><div><span class=\"section-label text-gold/60 mb-3 block\">Livrables</span><ul class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><li class=\"font-body text-[13px] text-white/65 border border-white/[0.12] rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 bg-white/[0.04]\">Dossiers conformes</li><li class=\"font-body text-[13px] text-white/65 border border-white/[0.12] rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 bg-white/[0.04]\">Déclarations déposées</li><li class=\"font-body text-[13px] text-white/65 border border-white/[0.12] rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 bg-white/[0.04]\">Rapports intermédiaires</li></ul></div></div></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 px-12 lg:px-20\" style=\"width:100vw\"><div class=\"max-w-2xl w-full\"><p class=\"font-display leading-none text-white/[0.035] select-none -mb-6\" style=\"font-size:clamp(5rem, 12vw, 9rem)\" aria-hidden=\"true\">04</p><h3 class=\"font-body text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-light text-white mb-5 leading-[1.2]\">Suivi continu</h3><div class=\"h-px w-10 bg-gold/50 mb-6\"></div><p class=\"font-body text-white/55 text-base leading-relaxed mb-8\">Notre engagement ne s&#x27;arrête pas à la mission initiale. Nous restons votre partenaire au quotidien, disponibles pour répondre à vos questions et anticiper les évolutions de votre situation.</p><div><span class=\"section-label text-gold/60 mb-3 block\">Livrables</span><ul class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><li class=\"font-body text-[13px] text-white/65 border border-white/[0.12] rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 bg-white/[0.04]\">Veille réglementaire</li><li class=\"font-body text-[13px] text-white/65 border border-white/[0.12] rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 bg-white/[0.04]\">Revues périodiques</li><li class=\"font-body text-[13px] text-white/65 border border-white/[0.12] rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 bg-white/[0.04]\">Conseil permanent</li></ul></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"container-main pb-14 mt-14 shrink-0\"><div class=\"flex justify-between mb-8 px-1\"><span class=\"font-body text-sm font-semibold leading-tight text-center transition-all duration-500 ease-out w-[25%] text-white/95 opacity-100 translate-y-0\" aria-hidden=\"false\">Premier contact</span><span class=\"font-body text-sm font-semibold leading-tight text-center transition-all duration-500 ease-out w-[25%] text-white/0 opacity-0 translate-y-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\">Analyse &amp; Stratégie</span><span class=\"font-body text-sm font-semibold leading-tight text-center transition-all duration-500 ease-out w-[25%] text-white/0 opacity-0 translate-y-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\">Mise en œuvre</span><span class=\"font-body text-sm font-semibold leading-tight text-center transition-all duration-500 ease-out w-[25%] text-white/0 opacity-0 translate-y-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\">Suivi continu</span></div><div class=\"relative flex items-center justify-between\"><div class=\"absolute top-1/2 left-0 right-0 h-px -translate-y-1/2 bg-white/[0.10]\"></div><div class=\"absolute top-1/2 left-0 h-px -translate-y-1/2 bg-gold/60 transition-all duration-500 ease-out\" style=\"width:0%\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center rounded-full font-body font-bold tabular-nums transition-all duration-500 ease-out w-11 h-11 text-[13px] bg-primary-500 text-white shadow-[0_0_0_5px_rgba(48,27,74,0.30)]\">01</div></div><div class=\"relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center rounded-full font-body font-bold tabular-nums transition-all duration-500 ease-out w-8 h-8 text-[11px] bg-white/10 text-white/35\">02</div></div><div class=\"relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center rounded-full font-body font-bold tabular-nums transition-all duration-500 ease-out w-8 h-8 text-[11px] bg-white/10 text-white/35\">03</div></div><div class=\"relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center rounded-full font-body font-bold tabular-nums transition-all duration-500 ease-out w-8 h-8 text-[11px] bg-white/10 text-white/35\">04</div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"md:hidden relative z-20 container-main pt-28 pb-16\"><div class=\"text-center mb-12\"><span class=\"section-label text-gold/70\">Notre approche</span><h2 class=\"font-display font-light text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl leading-[1.15] tracking-[-0.01em] text-white mt-2\">Un accompagnement<!-- --> <span class=\"italic font-light text-champagne\">structuré</span></h2></div><div class=\"space-y-4\"><div class=\"bg-white/[0.04] border border-white/[0.08] rounded-[24px] p-7\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-5\"><div class=\"w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-primary-500 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-body font-bold text-[10px] shrink-0\">01</div><div class=\"h-px flex-1 bg-white/[0.08]\"></div></div><h3 class=\"font-body text-xl font-light text-white mb-3 leading-[1.25]\">Premier contact</h3><div class=\"h-px w-8 bg-gold/40 mb-4\"></div><p class=\"font-body text-sm text-white/55 leading-relaxed mb-6\">Nous prenons le temps de comprendre votre situation, vos objectifs et vos contraintes. Un premier entretien sans engagement vous permet d&#x27;exposer vos besoins et de découvrir notre approche.</p><span class=\"section-label text-gold/60 mb-3 block\">Livrables</span><ul class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><li class=\"font-body text-[12px] text-white/60 border border-white/[0.10] rounded-full px-3 py-1 bg-white/[0.04]\">Diagnostic initial</li><li class=\"font-body text-[12px] text-white/60 border border-white/[0.10] rounded-full px-3 py-1 bg-white/[0.04]\">Proposition sur mesure</li><li class=\"font-body text-[12px] text-white/60 border border-white/[0.10] rounded-full px-3 py-1 bg-white/[0.04]\">Devis transparent</li></ul></div><div class=\"bg-white/[0.04] border border-white/[0.08] rounded-[24px] p-7\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-5\"><div class=\"w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-primary-500 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-body font-bold text-[10px] shrink-0\">02</div><div class=\"h-px flex-1 bg-white/[0.08]\"></div></div><h3 class=\"font-body text-xl font-light text-white mb-3 leading-[1.25]\">Analyse &amp; Stratégie</h3><div class=\"h-px w-8 bg-gold/40 mb-4\"></div><p class=\"font-body text-sm text-white/55 leading-relaxed mb-6\">Nos experts analysent votre situation financière, fiscale et administrative en profondeur. Nous définissons ensemble la stratégie optimale pour atteindre vos objectifs dans les meilleures conditions.</p><span class=\"section-label text-gold/60 mb-3 block\">Livrables</span><ul class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><li class=\"font-body text-[12px] text-white/60 border border-white/[0.10] rounded-full px-3 py-1 bg-white/[0.04]\">Rapport d&#x27;analyse</li><li class=\"font-body text-[12px] text-white/60 border border-white/[0.10] rounded-full px-3 py-1 bg-white/[0.04]\">Plan d&#x27;action détaillé</li><li class=\"font-body text-[12px] text-white/60 border border-white/[0.10] rounded-full px-3 py-1 bg-white/[0.04]\">Calendrier d&#x27;exécution</li></ul></div><div class=\"bg-white/[0.04] border border-white/[0.08] rounded-[24px] p-7\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-5\"><div class=\"w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-primary-500 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-body font-bold text-[10px] shrink-0\">03</div><div class=\"h-px flex-1 bg-white/[0.08]\"></div></div><h3 class=\"font-body text-xl font-light text-white mb-3 leading-[1.25]\">Mise en œuvre</h3><div class=\"h-px w-8 bg-gold/40 mb-4\"></div><p class=\"font-body text-sm text-white/55 leading-relaxed mb-6\">Nous exécutons le plan d&#x27;action avec rigueur et dans les délais convenus. Vous bénéficiez d&#x27;un suivi régulier et d&#x27;une communication proactive à chaque étape clé de la mission.</p><span class=\"section-label text-gold/60 mb-3 block\">Livrables</span><ul class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><li class=\"font-body text-[12px] text-white/60 border border-white/[0.10] rounded-full px-3 py-1 bg-white/[0.04]\">Dossiers conformes</li><li class=\"font-body text-[12px] text-white/60 border border-white/[0.10] rounded-full px-3 py-1 bg-white/[0.04]\">Déclarations déposées</li><li class=\"font-body text-[12px] text-white/60 border border-white/[0.10] rounded-full px-3 py-1 bg-white/[0.04]\">Rapports intermédiaires</li></ul></div><div class=\"bg-white/[0.04] border border-white/[0.08] rounded-[24px] p-7\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-5\"><div class=\"w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-primary-500 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-body font-bold text-[10px] shrink-0\">04</div><div class=\"h-px flex-1 bg-white/[0.08]\"></div></div><h3 class=\"font-body text-xl font-light text-white mb-3 leading-[1.25]\">Suivi continu</h3><div class=\"h-px w-8 bg-gold/40 mb-4\"></div><p class=\"font-body text-sm text-white/55 leading-relaxed mb-6\">Notre engagement ne s&#x27;arrête pas à la mission initiale. Nous restons votre partenaire au quotidien, disponibles pour répondre à vos questions et anticiper les évolutions de votre situation.</p><span class=\"section-label text-gold/60 mb-3 block\">Livrables</span><ul class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><li class=\"font-body text-[12px] text-white/60 border border-white/[0.10] rounded-full px-3 py-1 bg-white/[0.04]\">Veille réglementaire</li><li class=\"font-body text-[12px] text-white/60 border border-white/[0.10] rounded-full px-3 py-1 bg-white/[0.04]\">Revues périodiques</li><li class=\"font-body text-[12px] text-white/60 border border-white/[0.10] rounded-full px-3 py-1 bg-white/[0.04]\">Conseil permanent</li></ul></div></div></div></section><section class=\"relative bg-cream py-20 sm:py-28 lg:py-32 overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"container-main\"><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-premium overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"hidden lg:grid lg:grid-cols-[45fr_55fr]\"><div class=\"relative flex items-center justify-center bg-primary-50 p-6 xl:p-8 min-h-[480px]\"><div class=\"absolute -top-10 -left-10 w-64 h-64 rounded-full bg-primary-100 blur-3xl opacity-50\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><div class=\"absolute -bottom-8 -right-8 w-56 h-56 rounded-full bg-accent-50 blur-3xl opacity-60\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10 w-full aspect-square flex items-center justify-center\"><img alt=\"\" aria-hidden=\"true\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"w-full h-full object-contain drop-shadow-2xl scale-110\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fcheck-list.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fcheck-list.png&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fcheck-list.png&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75\"/></div></div><div class=\"p-10 xl:p-14 flex flex-col justify-center\"><span class=\"section-label\">Questions fréquentes</span><h2 class=\"font-display font-light text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl leading-[1.15] tracking-[-0.01em] text-navy mt-2 mb-3\">Vos questions,<!-- --> <span class=\"italic font-light text-champagne\">nos réponses</span></h2><p class=\"section-subtitle mb-10\">Tout ce que vous devez savoir avant de nous confier votre dossier.</p><div class=\"divide-y divide-gray-100\"><div><button type=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"true\" class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-between gap-4 py-5 text-left font-body font-semibold text-[15px] leading-snug transition-colors duration-200 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-primary-500 rounded text-primary-600\"><span>Combien coûte une déclaration d&#x27;impôts ?</span><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-7 h-7 rounded-full border-2 flex items-center justify-center transition-all duration-300 ease-smooth border-primary-500 bg-primary-500 text-white rotate-45\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg width=\"11\" height=\"11\" viewBox=\"0 0 11 11\" fill=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5.5 1v9M1 5.5h9\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path></svg></span></button><div class=\"grid transition-[grid-template-rows] duration-300 ease-smooth\" style=\"grid-template-rows:1fr\"><div class=\"overflow-hidden\"><p class=\"font-body text-sm sm:text-[15px] text-muted leading-relaxed pb-5 pr-10 transition-opacity duration-200 opacity-100\">Nos honoraires dépendent de la complexité de votre situation fiscale et du type de déclaration concernée (personne physique, société, succession). Nous établissons systématiquement un devis transparent avant toute mission. N&#x27;hésitez pas à nous contacter pour un entretien préliminaire sans engagement.</p></div></div></div><div><button type=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-between gap-4 py-5 text-left font-body font-semibold text-[15px] leading-snug transition-colors duration-200 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-primary-500 rounded text-ink hover:text-primary-600\"><span>Quels documents dois-je fournir ?</span><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-7 h-7 rounded-full border-2 flex items-center justify-center transition-all duration-300 ease-smooth border-gray-200 text-muted hover:border-primary-300\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg width=\"11\" height=\"11\" viewBox=\"0 0 11 11\" fill=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5.5 1v9M1 5.5h9\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path></svg></span></button><div class=\"grid transition-[grid-template-rows] duration-300 ease-smooth\" style=\"grid-template-rows:0fr\"><div class=\"overflow-hidden\"><p class=\"font-body text-sm sm:text-[15px] text-muted leading-relaxed pb-5 pr-10 transition-opacity duration-200 opacity-0\">La liste varie selon votre profil, mais inclut généralement : certificats de salaire, relevés bancaires et de prévoyance, attestations d&#x27;assurance, titres de propriété et tout document relatif à vos revenus et déductions. Après un premier échange, nous vous communiquons une liste personnalisée et précise.</p></div></div></div><div><button type=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-between gap-4 py-5 text-left font-body font-semibold text-[15px] leading-snug transition-colors duration-200 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-primary-500 rounded text-ink hover:text-primary-600\"><span>Combien de temps prend le traitement ?</span><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-7 h-7 rounded-full border-2 flex items-center justify-center transition-all duration-300 ease-smooth border-gray-200 text-muted hover:border-primary-300\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg width=\"11\" height=\"11\" viewBox=\"0 0 11 11\" fill=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5.5 1v9M1 5.5h9\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path></svg></span></button><div class=\"grid transition-[grid-template-rows] duration-300 ease-smooth\" style=\"grid-template-rows:0fr\"><div class=\"overflow-hidden\"><p class=\"font-body text-sm sm:text-[15px] text-muted leading-relaxed pb-5 pr-10 transition-opacity duration-200 opacity-0\">Pour une déclaration fiscale standard, comptez en moyenne 2 à 4 semaines après réception de l&#x27;ensemble des documents. Les dossiers plus complexes font l&#x27;objet d&#x27;un calendrier défini en amont avec vous. Nous vous informons à chaque étape clé du traitement.</p></div></div></div><div><button type=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-between gap-4 py-5 text-left font-body font-semibold text-[15px] leading-snug transition-colors duration-200 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-primary-500 rounded text-ink hover:text-primary-600\"><span>Puis-je planifier un rendez-vous ?</span><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-7 h-7 rounded-full border-2 flex items-center justify-center transition-all duration-300 ease-smooth border-gray-200 text-muted hover:border-primary-300\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg width=\"11\" height=\"11\" viewBox=\"0 0 11 11\" fill=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5.5 1v9M1 5.5h9\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path></svg></span></button><div class=\"grid transition-[grid-template-rows] duration-300 ease-smooth\" style=\"grid-template-rows:0fr\"><div class=\"overflow-hidden\"><p class=\"font-body text-sm sm:text-[15px] text-muted leading-relaxed pb-5 pr-10 transition-opacity duration-200 opacity-0\">Absolument. Nous proposons des entretiens en cabinet à Genève ou Lausanne, ainsi que des consultations en visioconférence. Le premier entretien est sans engagement et vous permet d&#x27;exposer votre situation en toute sérénité. Contactez-nous via notre formulaire ou par téléphone pour convenir d&#x27;un créneau.</p></div></div></div><div><button type=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-between gap-4 py-5 text-left font-body font-semibold text-[15px] leading-snug transition-colors duration-200 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-primary-500 rounded text-ink hover:text-primary-600\"><span>Est-ce confidentiel ?</span><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-7 h-7 rounded-full border-2 flex items-center justify-center transition-all duration-300 ease-smooth border-gray-200 text-muted hover:border-primary-300\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg width=\"11\" height=\"11\" viewBox=\"0 0 11 11\" fill=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5.5 1v9M1 5.5h9\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path></svg></span></button><div class=\"grid transition-[grid-template-rows] duration-300 ease-smooth\" style=\"grid-template-rows:0fr\"><div class=\"overflow-hidden\"><p class=\"font-body text-sm sm:text-[15px] text-muted leading-relaxed pb-5 pr-10 transition-opacity duration-200 opacity-0\">La confidentialité est un principe fondamental de notre profession. Toutes les informations que vous nous confiez sont protégées par le secret professionnel et traitées avec la plus grande discrétion. Vos données ne sont jamais partagées avec des tiers sans votre accord explicite.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"lg:hidden\"><div class=\"relative flex items-center justify-center bg-primary-50 py-12 px-8\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-primary-50\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10 w-52 h-52 flex items-center justify-center\"><img alt=\"\" aria-hidden=\"true\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"260\" height=\"260\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"w-full h-full object-contain drop-shadow-xl\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fcheck-list.png&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fcheck-list.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fcheck-list.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75\"/></div></div><div class=\"p-7 sm:p-10\"><div class=\"text-center mb-10\"><span class=\"section-label\">Questions fréquentes</span><h2 class=\"font-display font-light text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl leading-[1.15] tracking-[-0.01em] text-navy mt-2 mb-3\">Vos questions,<!-- --> <span class=\"italic font-light text-champagne\">nos réponses</span></h2><p class=\"section-subtitle mx-auto text-center\">Tout ce que vous devez savoir avant de nous confier votre dossier.</p></div><div class=\"divide-y divide-gray-100\"><div><button type=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"true\" class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-between gap-4 py-5 text-left font-body font-semibold text-[15px] leading-snug transition-colors duration-200 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-primary-500 rounded text-primary-600\"><span>Combien coûte une déclaration d&#x27;impôts ?</span><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-7 h-7 rounded-full border-2 flex items-center justify-center transition-all duration-300 ease-smooth border-primary-500 bg-primary-500 text-white rotate-45\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg width=\"11\" height=\"11\" viewBox=\"0 0 11 11\" fill=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5.5 1v9M1 5.5h9\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path></svg></span></button><div class=\"grid transition-[grid-template-rows] duration-300 ease-smooth\" style=\"grid-template-rows:1fr\"><div class=\"overflow-hidden\"><p class=\"font-body text-sm sm:text-[15px] text-muted leading-relaxed pb-5 pr-10 transition-opacity duration-200 opacity-100\">Nos honoraires dépendent de la complexité de votre situation fiscale et du type de déclaration concernée (personne physique, société, succession). Nous établissons systématiquement un devis transparent avant toute mission. N&#x27;hésitez pas à nous contacter pour un entretien préliminaire sans engagement.</p></div></div></div><div><button type=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-between gap-4 py-5 text-left font-body font-semibold text-[15px] leading-snug transition-colors duration-200 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-primary-500 rounded text-ink hover:text-primary-600\"><span>Quels documents dois-je fournir ?</span><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-7 h-7 rounded-full border-2 flex items-center justify-center transition-all duration-300 ease-smooth border-gray-200 text-muted hover:border-primary-300\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg width=\"11\" height=\"11\" viewBox=\"0 0 11 11\" fill=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5.5 1v9M1 5.5h9\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path></svg></span></button><div class=\"grid transition-[grid-template-rows] duration-300 ease-smooth\" style=\"grid-template-rows:0fr\"><div class=\"overflow-hidden\"><p class=\"font-body text-sm sm:text-[15px] text-muted leading-relaxed pb-5 pr-10 transition-opacity duration-200 opacity-0\">La liste varie selon votre profil, mais inclut généralement : certificats de salaire, relevés bancaires et de prévoyance, attestations d&#x27;assurance, titres de propriété et tout document relatif à vos revenus et déductions. Après un premier échange, nous vous communiquons une liste personnalisée et précise.</p></div></div></div><div><button type=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-between gap-4 py-5 text-left font-body font-semibold text-[15px] leading-snug transition-colors duration-200 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-primary-500 rounded text-ink hover:text-primary-600\"><span>Combien de temps prend le traitement ?</span><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-7 h-7 rounded-full border-2 flex items-center justify-center transition-all duration-300 ease-smooth border-gray-200 text-muted hover:border-primary-300\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg width=\"11\" height=\"11\" viewBox=\"0 0 11 11\" fill=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5.5 1v9M1 5.5h9\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path></svg></span></button><div class=\"grid transition-[grid-template-rows] duration-300 ease-smooth\" style=\"grid-template-rows:0fr\"><div class=\"overflow-hidden\"><p class=\"font-body text-sm sm:text-[15px] text-muted leading-relaxed pb-5 pr-10 transition-opacity duration-200 opacity-0\">Pour une déclaration fiscale standard, comptez en moyenne 2 à 4 semaines après réception de l&#x27;ensemble des documents. Les dossiers plus complexes font l&#x27;objet d&#x27;un calendrier défini en amont avec vous. Nous vous informons à chaque étape clé du traitement.</p></div></div></div><div><button type=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-between gap-4 py-5 text-left font-body font-semibold text-[15px] leading-snug transition-colors duration-200 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-primary-500 rounded text-ink hover:text-primary-600\"><span>Puis-je planifier un rendez-vous ?</span><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-7 h-7 rounded-full border-2 flex items-center justify-center transition-all duration-300 ease-smooth border-gray-200 text-muted hover:border-primary-300\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg width=\"11\" height=\"11\" viewBox=\"0 0 11 11\" fill=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5.5 1v9M1 5.5h9\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path></svg></span></button><div class=\"grid transition-[grid-template-rows] duration-300 ease-smooth\" style=\"grid-template-rows:0fr\"><div class=\"overflow-hidden\"><p class=\"font-body text-sm sm:text-[15px] text-muted leading-relaxed pb-5 pr-10 transition-opacity duration-200 opacity-0\">Absolument. Nous proposons des entretiens en cabinet à Genève ou Lausanne, ainsi que des consultations en visioconférence. Le premier entretien est sans engagement et vous permet d&#x27;exposer votre situation en toute sérénité. Contactez-nous via notre formulaire ou par téléphone pour convenir d&#x27;un créneau.</p></div></div></div><div><button type=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-between gap-4 py-5 text-left font-body font-semibold text-[15px] leading-snug transition-colors duration-200 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-primary-500 rounded text-ink hover:text-primary-600\"><span>Est-ce confidentiel ?</span><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-7 h-7 rounded-full border-2 flex items-center justify-center transition-all duration-300 ease-smooth border-gray-200 text-muted hover:border-primary-300\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg width=\"11\" height=\"11\" viewBox=\"0 0 11 11\" fill=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5.5 1v9M1 5.5h9\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path></svg></span></button><div class=\"grid transition-[grid-template-rows] duration-300 ease-smooth\" style=\"grid-template-rows:0fr\"><div class=\"overflow-hidden\"><p class=\"font-body text-sm sm:text-[15px] text-muted leading-relaxed pb-5 pr-10 transition-opacity duration-200 opacity-0\">La confidentialité est un principe fondamental de notre profession. Toutes les informations que vous nous confiez sont protégées par le secret professionnel et traitées avec la plus grande discrétion. Vos données ne sont jamais partagées avec des tiers sans votre accord explicite.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"contact\" class=\"relative w-full overflow-hidden bg-stone\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 1440 80\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute top-0 left-0 w-full pointer-events-none z-0\" style=\"height:var(--slant-h)\"><polygon points=\"0,0 1440,0 1440,80\" fill=\"#F8F9FC\"></polygon></svg><div class=\"relative z-10 container-main pt-32 sm:pt-40 pb-28 sm:pb-36\"><div class=\"max-w-2xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"text-center mb-12\"><span class=\"section-label\">Contactez-nous</span><h2 class=\"section-title\">Parlons de votre projet</h2><p class=\"section-subtitle mx-auto text-center mt-4\">Remplissez le formulaire ci-dessous et nous vous répondrons dans les 24 heures ouvrables.</p><p class=\"font-body text-[10.5px] tracking-[0.10em] uppercase text-muted/50 mt-4\">Réponse sous 24h ouvrables · Confidentialité garantie</p></div><form noValidate=\"\" class=\"bg-gradient-to-br from-white via-white to-primary-50/25 rounded-2xl border border-primary-100 shadow-premium p-8 sm:p-12\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-x-6 gap-y-1\"><div><label for=\"name\" class=\"block font-body text-[10.5px] tracking-[0.10em] uppercase font-semibold text-navy/55 mb-2\">Nom et prénom *</label><input id=\"name\" type=\"text\" autoComplete=\"name\" placeholder=\"Sophie Dupont\" aria-invalid=\"false\" class=\"w-full font-body text-sm text-ink bg-primary-50/40 border border-primary-200/60 rounded-xl px-4 py-3.5 transition-all duration-200 ease-smooth hover:border-primary-300/80 hover:bg-primary-50/70 placeholder:text-muted/35 focus:outline-none focus:border-gold/50 focus:bg-white focus:ring-2 focus:ring-gold/[0.10]\" name=\"name\" value=\"\"/><div class=\"mt-1.5 h-4\" role=\"alert\" aria-live=\"polite\"></div></div><div><label for=\"company\" class=\"block font-body text-[10.5px] tracking-[0.10em] uppercase font-semibold text-navy/55 mb-2\">Société</label><input id=\"company\" type=\"text\" autoComplete=\"organization\" placeholder=\"Ma Société Sàrl\" aria-invalid=\"false\" class=\"w-full font-body text-sm text-ink bg-primary-50/40 border border-primary-200/60 rounded-xl px-4 py-3.5 transition-all duration-200 ease-smooth hover:border-primary-300/80 hover:bg-primary-50/70 placeholder:text-muted/35 focus:outline-none focus:border-gold/50 focus:bg-white focus:ring-2 focus:ring-gold/[0.10]\" name=\"company\" value=\"\"/><div class=\"mt-1.5 h-4\" role=\"alert\" aria-live=\"polite\"></div></div><div><label for=\"email\" class=\"block font-body text-[10.5px] tracking-[0.10em] uppercase font-semibold text-navy/55 mb-2\">Adresse e-mail *</label><inp